  "system": {
    "description": "<p>Available at CR 11 or higher. The target gains a +[POW Mod] bonus to [Physical Defense] and [Magical Defense]. This effect lasts until the beginning of your next Main Process, or until the target leaves the square you are in.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>(SR2): Increase bonus to +[[POW Mod] + 4].</p>\n<p>(SR3): Increase bonus to +[[POW Mod] + 8].</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>Magic that creates a sanctuary that wards off disasters and protects nearby allies. No matter what kind of hostility swirls on the battlefield, the sanctuary becomes a haven.</p>",
